<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pengaturan Waktu - App_PADi</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#F8F9FA] flex">
    <aside class="w-64 h-screen bg-white border-r p-6 flex flex-col fixed">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#006652] mb-10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="bg-[#006652] w-8 h-8 rounded-lg"></div> Portal
        </div>
        <nav class="flex-1 space-y-2">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/daftar-siswa" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">Daftar Siswa</a>
            <a href="/daftar-guru" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">Daftar Guru</a>
            <a href="/jadwal" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-[#006652] text-white rounded-lg shadow-md">Jadwal</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="mt-auto border-t pt-4 space-y-2">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 text-red-500 font-medium">Log Out</a>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="flex-1 ml-64 p-10 flex gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border shadow-sm mb-2">
                <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-lg">Admin</span>
                <div class="relative w-72">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Cari Siswa atau Staff" class="w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-1.5 border rounded-full text-xs bg-gray-50 outline-none">
                    <span class="absolute left-3 top-2 opacity-30 text-xs">🔍</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#005c49] to-[#007a61] text-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Pengaturan Waktu</h2>
                <p class="text-green-100 text-sm max-w-xl mb-6">Rancang shift yang selaras dengan jam pelajaran siswa dan jadwal standar. Ketepatan waktu membangun disiplin profesional.</p>
                <button class="bg-orange-500 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold shadow-md hover:bg-orange-600 transition">
                    + Buat Jadwal
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 font-bold text-sm">
                    <span>🕒</span> <h3>Jadwal Aktif</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center hover:shadow-md transition">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-3 rounded-full text-teal-600 font-bold text-sm">AM</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Waktu Pembelajaran Pagi</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">📅 07:30 - 12:00 &nbsp;•&nbsp; 👥 8 Kelas</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 border border-white rounded-full text-[9px] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gray-500">X-A</div>
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-300 border border-white rounded-full text-[9px] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gray-500">XI-R1</div>
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-400 border border-white rounded-full text-[9px] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gray-500">XII-A</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600">✏️</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center hover:shadow-md transition">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-orange-50 p-3 rounded-full text-orange-600 font-bold text-sm">PM</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Waktu Pembelajaran Siang</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">📅 13:00 - 17:30 &nbsp;•&nbsp; 👥 5 Kelas</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 border border-white rounded-full text-[9px] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gray-500">XI-B</div>
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-300 border border-white rounded-full text-[9px] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gray-500">XII-B</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600">✏️</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border shadow-sm space-y-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Parameter Waktu</h3>
                    <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold">● Jadwal Aktif</span>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-gray-50/50">
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase">Check-In</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">📥</span>
                            <input type="text" value="07:00 AM" class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm bg-transparent outline-none w-full">
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[9px] text-gray-400 mt-1">Earliest scan time allowed</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-gray-50/50">
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase">Maks Terlambat</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="text-orange-500 text-sm">⚠️</span>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
                                <input type="text" value="15" class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm bg-transparent outline-none w-8 text-center">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Menit</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[9px] text-gray-400 mt-1">Grace period before 'Late'</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-gray-50/50">
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase">Checkout</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">📤</span>
                            <input type="text" value="12:00 PM" class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm bg-transparent outline-none w-full">
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[9px] text-gray-400 mt-1">Scan enabled for departure</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-end gap-3 pt-2">
                    <button class="px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Batalkan</button>
                    <button class="bg-[#006652] text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold shadow-sm">Update Jadwal</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4 text-[11px]">
                <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> <span class="text-gray-400">STATUS SISTEM:</span> <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">OPERATIONAL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="text-gray-400">🕒 PERUBAHAN TERAKHIR:</span> <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold">2j 14m yang lalu</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-72 space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Kelas Yang Belum Terjadwal</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5 mb-4">Drag and drop kelas</p>
                
                <span class="text-[10px] bg-gray-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold text-gray-500 tracking-wider">UNASSIGNED (4)</span>
                
                <div class="mt-3 border rounded-xl p-3 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white transition cursor-grab">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-400 text-base">🏫</span>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs">XI - B</p>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">32 Siswa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-gray-300 text-xs">:::</span>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-2 border rounded-xl p-3 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white transition cursor-grab">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-400 text-base">💻</span>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs">X - F</p>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">28 Siswa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-gray-300 text-xs">:::</span>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-2 border rounded-xl p-3 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white transition cursor-grab">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-gray-400 text-base">⚡</span>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs">XII - C</p>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">30 Siswa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-gray-300 text-xs">:::</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-orange-50/70 border border-orange-100 p-5 rounded-2xl space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-700 text-xs font-bold">
                    <span>ℹ️</span> <h4>Rotasi Mingguan</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-orange-800 leading-relaxed opacity-90">Sistem akan memutar jadwal secara otomatis. Shift setiap hari Senin untuk Semester 2 jadwal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>